==English==

{{rank|pale|happiness|religion|915|dress|degree|spoken|stop}}

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|[drɛs]}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# A [[garment]], item of [[clothing]] (usually worn by a woman) which covers the upper part of the body as well as below the waist.
# An [[apparel]], [[clothing]].

